## ``uscountygeojson``: US Counties map in Geojson format (list)

#### Description 

This data comes from the https://code.highcharts.com/mapdata/countries/us/us-all-all.
js and is used in highmaps examples.

#### Usage
<pre><code>
uscountygeojson
</code></pre>

#### Format

A list in geojson format.
